msgid "(Huh... A bathroom?)"
msgstr "（啊...这是一间洗手间吗？）"

msgid "Um... excuse me."
msgstr "额...不好意思。"

msgid "Could you wait outside?"
msgstr "请问你能出去一下么？"

msgid "Wha-? Oh. Of course."
msgstr "什—？哦。没问题。"

msgid "I- ...I guess I'll stay out there."
msgstr "我——...我会出去待着的。"

msgid "Scream if you need me."
msgstr "需要我的话就大声叫出来吧。"

msgid "...I won't."
msgstr "...我不会这么干的。"

msgid "(Now I get to have some time away from that guy.)"
msgstr "（现在我可以离开那家伙一段时间了。）"

msgid "(Is it really safe to have him around?)"
msgstr "（把他带在在身边真的安全吗？）"

msgid "(A bathroom?)"
msgstr "（这是一间洗手间吗？）"

msgid "(I hope that guy won't find me here.)"
msgstr "（希望那家伙不会发现我在这里。）"

msgid "(I don't really trust him... Hopefully he's not searching for me...)"
msgstr "（我无法真正相信他...希望他没有在找我...）"

msgid "(Hiro would tell me to have a bit of faith in others, but...)"
msgstr "（希罗告诉我对别人要有点信心，但是...）"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.event_hiro_call.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "(I wonder if I could ask Hiro.)"
msgstr "（我在想我是不是可以问问希罗。）"

msgid "(Is it even possible to call from here?)"
msgstr "（这里能打电话吗？）"

msgid "(I still have no signal... but... that didn't matter last time.)"
msgstr "（仍然没有信号...但...上次也打出去了。）"

msgid "Oh... I'm out of battery."
msgstr "哦...没电了。"

msgid "That's not good... I suppose using it as a flashlight killed it."
msgstr "这可不妙... 我想是把它当手电筒的时候用完了吧。"

msgid "...Oh well."
msgstr "...这下好了。"

msgid "I'll give it a try."
msgstr "我来试试吧。"

msgid "Lace!"
msgstr "小莱！"

msgid "Oh good..."
msgstr "哦，太好了..."

msgid "Thank goodness I can reach you, Hiro..."
msgstr "幸好我能联系到你，希罗..."

msgid "Are you alright!?"
msgstr "你还好吧！？"

msgid "What happened!?"
msgstr "发生什么事了！？"

msgid "Are you safe!?"
msgstr "你还安全吗！？"

msgid "Yes, I'm okay."
msgstr "是的，我还好。"

msgid "(Though I did fall down the stairs and wake up in some sort of dungeon...)"
msgstr "（虽然说我从楼梯上摔了下来，还在某种地牢里醒了过来...）"

msgid "(and there's a strange guy following me everywhere...)"
msgstr "（以及还有一个怪家伙在跟着我到处走...）"

msgid "(...and there was a strange guy following me everywhere...)"
msgstr "（...以及之前还有个怪家伙在跟着我到处走...）"

msgid "(...and Rune said there's no way out.)"
msgstr "（...还有符文说这里没有出去的办法。）"

msgid "Everything is okay, don't worry."
msgstr "一切都还好，不要担心。"

msgid "Thank god."
msgstr "感谢上帝。"

msgid "Is everything alright? Why are you whispering?"
msgstr "没事吧？你为什么小声说话？"

msgid "Because there's someone right outside, and..."
msgstr "因为这外面有个人，以及..."

msgid "Because someone might be looking for me."
msgstr "因为有个人可能在找我。"

msgid "An enemy!?"
msgstr "是敌人吗！？"

msgid "No, well... he says he's not."
msgstr "不，好吧...他说他不是。"

msgid "And now he's following me around."
msgstr "以及现在他正在跟着我走。"

msgid "You made a friend!?"
msgstr "你交了个朋友！？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.event_hiro_call.dlg.lacie"
msgid "No."
msgstr "不是的。"

msgid "I don't really trust him."
msgstr "我不能完全相信他。"

msgid "But maybe it's better to have company! He might be willing to tag along and help!"
msgstr "但是也许有人陪会更好呢！他也许愿意跟来帮忙！"

msgid "But... that's why it's strange."
msgstr "但是...这就是奇怪的地方啊。"

msgid "Why is he willing to tag along?"
msgstr "为什么他会愿意跟着我呢？"

msgid "...You know how people act around me, Hiro..."
msgstr "...你知道别人是怎么对我的，希罗..."

msgid "And he's just acting...like nothing is wrong with me."
msgstr "他只是在掩饰...像是我身上没有任何不对劲的地方。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.event_hiro_call.dlg.hiro"
msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr "嗯......"

msgid "You sound conflicted."
msgstr "听起来你很矛盾。"

msgid "Well... I don't really care, I just..."
msgstr "好吧...我不是真的在意这个，我只是觉得..."

msgid "He's just shady."
msgstr "他就是不三不四啊。"

msgid "Well, tell you what. It's your choice."
msgstr "好的，那就这样吧。这是你的选择。"

msgid "You can have him tag along and see how it plays out..."
msgstr "你可以让他跟着你，然后看他会怎么做..."

msgid "...or you can ditch him."
msgstr "...或者你也可以抛弃他。"

msgid "No, well... he said he's not."
msgstr "不，好吧...他说他不是。"

msgid "But... it doesn't matter. I already got rid of him."
msgstr "但...这不重要。我已经摆脱他了。"

msgid "Well, I can't condone murder but..."
msgstr "好吧，虽然我不能容忍这种谋杀行为，但是..."

msgid "No! Not like that! Hiro!"
msgstr "不！不是那样的！希罗！"

msgid "He's still somewhere around... I just slipped away for a bit."
msgstr "他还在附近...我只是溜走了一小会儿。"

msgid "Well, tell you what."
msgstr "好吧，这样讲吧。"

msgid "Next time he finds you, you could try locking him up somewhere."
msgstr "下次他找到你的时候，你可以把他锁在哪里。"

msgid "Huh... it's not like you to suggest something like that."
msgstr "呃...这可不像你提出的建议啊。"

msgid "Well, I personally think you should have a bit of faith in him! But it's up to you."
msgstr "其实，我个人认为，你应该对他有点信心！但这取决于你。"

msgid "Well, I personally think you could go back and apologize."
msgstr "其实，我个人认为，你可以回去道歉。"

msgid "Nothing wrong with making a friend, right? Still, it's up to you."
msgstr "交个朋友没什么不好吧？不过，这还是取决于你。"

msgid "(Yeah... that's more like it.)"
msgstr "（没错...这还差不多。）"

msgid "I should go."
msgstr "我该走了。"

msgid "Be careful, Lace."
msgstr "小心点啊，小莱。"

msgid "Get back home safely."
msgstr "要安全地回家啊。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.event_hiro_call.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "嗯。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.item_bucket_on_drain.dlg.sai"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "I can't believe I'm entertaining this idea."
msgstr "真不敢相信我竟然会有这种想法。"

msgid "This is the stupidest thing I've ever done."
msgstr "这是我做过最蠢的事情了。"

msgid "Just a few more trips!"
msgstr "再多跑几趟就好了！"

msgid "This'll work, you'll see."
msgstr "会有用的，你等着瞧吧。"

msgid "There's no way."
msgstr "怎么可能。"

msgid "At least this is a good workout."
msgstr "起码这也算一次不错的锻炼嘛。"

msgid "(I'm not fit enough for this...)"
msgstr "（我的身体还没好到可以做这种事...）"

msgid "Sigh... What makes you think the drain isn't connected to the water we're removing..."
msgstr "唉... 你怎么知道这个下水道跟我们要排走的水是不是连通的呢..."

msgid "Hm... I don't know."
msgstr "呃...我不知道。"

msgid "Well, too late to consider that now."
msgstr "好吧，现在考虑这个已经太晚了。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.item_bucket_on_drain.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "(What possessed me to agree to this?)"
msgstr "（到底是什么迫使我同意了这个想法？）"

msgid "We're really bonding over this, don't you think?"
msgstr "你不觉得我们真的很有默契吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.item_bucket_on_drain.dlg.lacie"
msgid "....."
msgstr "....."

msgid "One Eternity Later..."
msgstr "一世之后..."

msgid "You actually did it."
msgstr "你真的做到了。"

msgid "Congratulations!"
msgstr "恭喜！"

msgid "This is nothing. Just wait until you hear my other ideas."
msgstr "这还不算什么。就等着听我的其他点子吧。"

msgid "I very much look forward to it!"
msgstr "我很期待！"

msgid "Will she be okay?"
msgstr "她没事吗？"

msgid "She'll be fine."
msgstr "她会没事的。"

msgid "See? She's still breathing."
msgstr "看到了吗？她还在呼吸呢。"

msgid "Um... will you be okay?"
msgstr "唔...你没事吧？"

msgid "Nice! You're sturdy, aren't you?"
msgstr "太好了！你还挺结实的，是不是？"

msgid "You ready to go?"
msgstr "你准备好了吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.item_bucket_on_drain.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "嗯。"

msgid "A mop. It looks like it's never been used."
msgstr "一个拖把。看起来从来没用过。"

msgid "Everything here has been gathering dust for a really long time."
msgstr "这里的一切都尘封已久。"

msgid "There's something on this shelf."
msgstr "架子上有东西。"

msgid "There's nothing else of use."
msgstr "这里没有其他能用的东西了。"

msgid "A rusted sink."
msgstr "锈迹斑斑的水槽。"

msgid "A bathroom stall. It's occupied."
msgstr "一个厕所隔间。有人。"

msgid "Try to open it anyways?"
msgstr "无论如何，要试着打开它吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.misc_stall_6.choice.Try to open it anyways?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.misc_stall_6.choice.Try to open it anyways?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Something shiny can be seen at the bottom of the toilet bowl."
msgstr "在马桶底部可以看到一些闪闪发光的东西。"

msgid "Fish it out?"
msgstr "要捞出来吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.misc_toilet_3_coin.choice.Fish it out?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.misc_toilet_3_coin.choice.Fish it out?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "A small hand towel."
msgstr "一条小手帕。"

msgid "That took a million years."
msgstr "真是花了一百万年时间啊。"

msgid "Were you talking to someone in there?"
msgstr "刚才你是在里面跟谁说话吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.move_exit_sai.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.move_exit_sai.dlg.lacie"
msgid "No."
msgstr "没有。"

msgid "(Did he overhear anything...?)"
msgstr "（他有没有偷听到什么...？）"

msgid "It kinda sounded like it."
msgstr "看起来还真是这样。"

msgid "I wasn't."
msgstr "真的没有。"

msgid "Oh."
msgstr "好吧。"

msgid "It's cool, I talk to myself sometimes too."
msgstr "没事的，我有时候也会自言自语。"

msgid "Like having a little narrator, right?"
msgstr "就像有个小旁白在讲，对吧？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Bathroom.move_exit_sai.dlg.lacie"
msgid "....."
msgstr "....."

msgid "Find anything cool?"
msgstr "找到什么有趣的东西了吗？"

msgid "Nope."
msgstr "没。"

msgid "...Where did you get that?"
msgstr "...你从哪儿弄来的？"

msgid "The lollipop? I had 'em with me."
msgstr "棒棒糖吗？我随身带着。"

msgid "Want some?"
msgstr "你要吗？"

msgid "I don't accept candy from strangers."
msgstr "我不想要陌生人给的糖。"

msgid "(Sai joined your party.)"
msgstr "（赛伊加入了你的队伍。）"
